Uses of Package
gpsSystem

  • Classes in gpsSystem used by gpsSystem 
    Class Description
    GPS
    Interface that provides functionalities for adding a street or a restriction in memory, and driving between two points
    Map
    the Map class, that stores a graph of all streets and points, and implements GPS interface for adding streets, restrictions and driving
    Point
    The point class, which implements Comparable interface for using the priority queue structure.
    Restriction
    Specific restriction that can appear on one street, like accidents or traffic jams
    Street
    The street class, that acts like a vertex from the start point to the end point It has a speed limit, a gauge limit and a list of roadblocks
    Vehicle
    Abstract vehicle class, extended by bicycle, motorcycle, car, truck
